content:
With the introduction of the new tax solution that automatically calculates tax, we renamed the existing Salesforce Tax Solution to Manual Salesforce Tax Solution. The new automatic tax solution is now named Salesforce Tax Solution. Based on how you want to set up your taxes, you can choose either solution. Salesforce Tax Solution is available only with Salesforce checkout. Manual Salesforce Tax Solution is available only with custom checkout.

Where: This change applies to B2B Commerce and D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: To switch to Manual Salesforce Tax Solution, on the Checkout Configuration page, click Use Custom Checkout. You canâ€™t use the new Salesforce solution after you switch to Manual Salesforce Tax Solution.
title: Manual Salesforce Tax Solution
